        <updateDate>2021-03-01T21:12:27Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Disclose Police Brutality Bonds Act of 2020 </b></p> <p>This bill requires issuers of securities to disclose services provided to state and local governments related to the issuance of bonds if proceeds may be used to pay settlements or judgments in connection with police violence or civil rights abuses. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
